## Case 1: Regex Patterns with Modifiers
|/^[a-z0-9_-]+ /| gi;

## Case 2: Pattern in Dispatch
$input |> |/\d+/| ( "Match found!" );

## Case 3: Pattern Fields (Dynamic Patterns)
+ |/^user_{ $id }_pattern /|: "Match";

## Case 4: Complex Pattern Dispatch
/users/name |> |/^[A-Z][a-z]+ /| [ //info ] { !!("Name valid") };
